<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Bienvenue Ã  la JVLAN</h1>
    <p class="lead">Connecte-toi avec ton compte Steam pour commencer.</p>
    <p>
        <a href="/auth/steam"><img src="https://steamcommunity-a.akamaihd.net/public/images/signinthroughsteam/sits_large_noborder.png" alt="Sign in using Steam"></a>
    </p>
    <br/>
    <p class="lead">Si tu n'as pas de compte steam, viens voir les admins - en particulier Poli.</p>
    <p>
      <div class="form-inline">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="loginUsername">Nom d'utilisateur</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="loginUsername" maxlength="24">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="loginCode">Code</label>
          <input type="email" class="form-control" id="loginCode" placeholder="ex. ababa" size="8" maxlength="5">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default" onclick="loginWithCode()">Se connecter</button>
      </div>
      <script>
      function loginWithCode() {
          var username = $('#loginUsername').val().trim();
          var code = $('#loginCode').val().trim();

          //if code is blank, attempt dev loginCode
          if (code === '') {
              window.location.href = '/devlogin?username=' + username;
          } else {
              window.location.href = '/login?username=' + username + '&code=' + code;
          }
      }
      </script>
    </p>
</div>
